data.description:
Arcadia Resorts is the family-owned, exclusive vacation membership company and part of the New Hotel Collection family. We own four of our own resorts & hotels properties around the country ... and we are on our way to purchasing our fifth! 

Two of our properties are located in the Clearwater/St. Petersburg Florida area: Harbourside Resort is located in charming Indian Rocks Beach, Beachside Resort, which directly faces Indian Shores beach, the New Hotel Collection Smoky Mountains in Sevierville, TN. In 1923, and our newest addition, The Cordova Inn, a historic boutique hotel located in downtown St. Pete, FL that will soon become one of downtown's largest and most exclusive resorts on the gulf coast. 

Arcadia Resorts Membership Club offers an innovative and exclusive vacation program. Unlike traditional timeshare and travel clubs, Arcadia’s exclusive Membership offers its members guaranteed choice, flexibility, and availability to vacation any time of year to any of RCIs 4,500 five-star resorts around the world. No hidden fees, no binding deeds, no blackout dates - - just simple, affordable vacations - - it's that simple!

GROWING, THRIVING, & HIRING!

Do you envision yourself working within a supportive, growing company? Are you interested in working for a rising star in the hospitality, travel, & leisure business? Have you ever wondered how you can apply your personal strengths to create a lasting career? Do you value opportunities for growth and leadership? 

Arcadia Resorts is in an exciting growth phase; hiring a variety of professionals. We train, support, & value all of our employees & pride ourselves on our positive culture by ensuring the personal and professional success of everyone in our Arcadia family!

Learn more about your place in our amazing Arcadia Resorts family! Let's make your professional dreams come true! #hiring #travel #resume #hospitality #career #growth #sales
